name: Tansocc Test
description: 【Carbon Meta】is a new metaverse collaborative symbiosis platform developed by Zhongshu Carbonben (Xiamen) Metaverse Technology Co., Ltd. The Carbon Meta platform focuses on the core technology of new productive forces and leverages non-fungible tokens (NFTs) to promote the digital application of digital property certificates. It helps enterprises establish brand influence and form positive interactions between the enterprise brand and enterprise co-builders (users). This allows users to share in the monetization of attention economy value and achieve value sharing between enterprises and users. In addition, Carbon Meta provides extensive Web3.0 scenarios with digital RMB, including digital identity authentication, digital property certificate NFTs, metaverse social networking, community voting governance, and more. It changes the traditional transactional relationship between enterprises and users, creating a digital community of high-quality development and shared prosperity.
